storyInfo: Hearing there's an abandoned plate she can hit, Toddifons joins in giddy with glee and man-portable siege ballista in tow. However, she only notices upon reaching the mission site that things may not have been quite as she was fancying.

attributes.content: Left!
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Ugh!
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Oi, Phidia—
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Me and the Raging Ironhide ARE on your left!
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: I meant, fortcrackers dropping on your left—
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: You're in my artillery's way.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Phidia, you still alive?
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: ...*cough* *cough*...
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Seriously, I've never had a fight this difficult before.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: You're a real sturdy rotter, aren't you? Yeah, okay, I think it's the explosion just touched you. Not much real damages I can tell.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Maybe I should up my fortcracker charges, 20%-some?
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Then I'm never going on a mission with you again.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Hmm... joint #3's hydraulic systems aren't stable anymore. You're paying for maintenance.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: You can't blame me—your mech's horrible for visibility. Honestly, it's only fair I let the siege-ballista do it in one of these days.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Should try if we get the chance, really. Ought to blast straight through, I think?
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: On my pride as a Tiacauh, next intra-department meeting, I'm voting down your budget.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Well, that's a bloody joke! Do you understand the importance of siege weapons?!
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: My master says Rhodes Island isn't installing siege weapons of any kind. It's not in accordance with our founding principles.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: But honestly? This giant bow of yours doesn't even count as siege weaponry.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Wha...?! A man-portable siege ballista's still a siege ballista!
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: It's a bow that doesn't even have an engine.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Bows never HAD engines! And it's a BALLISTA!
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Sorry, my tribe's bows had engines.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: You want to go, Phidia?
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: My name's Zumama.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Hey, we're right here, you know?!
attributes.name: Agama Gang

attributes.content: Shut up!
attributes.name: Toddifons & Eunectes

attributes.content: Aaargh!
attributes.name: Agama Gang

attributes.content: Then let's see if your heaping pile of scrap can take a fortcracker shot for real!
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Bring it on!
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Um... excuse me?
attributes.name: Wastelander

attributes.content: Are you soft? We're busy here.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: You two are Rhodes Islanders?
attributes.name: Wastelander

attributes.content: And you are...?
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Ah, just to warn you by the way, I think that ballista had its right-side torsion hookup worn out in combat just now. Your accuracy's going to suffer if you keep making it work.
attributes.name: Wastelander

attributes.content: Tch!
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: The... um... yellow tractor there?
attributes.name: Wastelander

attributes.content: You can call her the Raging Ironhide.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: You'd better take a look at the state of her cooling systems. Put that off any longer, and you'll get funny sounds from the engine.
attributes.name: Wastelander

attributes.content: You're right! Thanks, uh...
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Call me Rickety Joe. Nice to meet you, Rhodes Islanders.
attributes.name: Wastelander

attributes.content: I commissioned this here mission.
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: Is your op unit... just the two of you?
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: Don't trust our professional ability?
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Of course I do. Sesa recommended you, after all. Rhodes Island's name... is plenty well-known among wastelanders.
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: But, uh, I have to say, you two are...
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: Haha... There's definitely been some mishaps...
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Keep traveling for about an hour, and you'll be at the point where intel says the abandoned plate is.
attributes.name: Field Operator

attributes.content: Toddifons, Eunectes, how's your equipment checks?
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: Phew. Just finished loading everything into the truck.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: The Raging Ironhide's in fine condition. I gave her a total upgrade with my master earlier, and the driver's seat is a lot more comfortable now.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Oh, yeah, I haven't seen that weird little Liberi around for this mission...
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: The High Priest said I can't always count on him to drive. It's my mech, after all.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Well, no complaints here, I'll take you driving any day... Everything okay with the siege ballista, Toddifons?
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: Ugh, classic. The Doctor said there was an abandoned plate I could go hit, so I rock up.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: And this turns out to be a rescue mission?!
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: You only just now realized?
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: Hah—I spent three nights in a row up for this mission, rushing a batch of superheavy-duty fortcracker arrows! And you're telling me I'm rescuing the barreners on that stupid plate?!
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Toddifons... next time, make sure to read the mission brief beforehand?
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: There's a chance hostiles encamped the plate, in which case they've got defenses to counter with. You're good for assaulting fortified positions. That's why I asked the Doc to send you, just in case.
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: Even if we're taking on an abandoned plate, it still used to be a part of a nomadic city. It's always good to bring heavy arms.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: *sigh* Would've gone out to town if I knew. Bloody end me—
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Apparently these wastelanders have been moving with the nomadic city for a long while, just gritting their teeth waiting for a plate to get scrapped. They were hoping they could breathe easy for a few days with it, and find some supplies in there.
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: Turned out 'Mama John's' and the local pasha had a reclamation contract signed already.
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: Heh. They like to do their business direct. Nothing's changed.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: We'll rendezvous at the Canning intersection. We're coming from southwest...
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: 'Scuse me, Blaze. Doesn't visibility seem a little low to you?
attributes.name: Field Operator

attributes.content: Wind's funny...
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Abnormal weather up ahead!
attributes.name: Field Operator

attributes.content: We see the sandstorm from our vehicle too!
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Tha... That's gathering fast! Get in the truck!
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Message from the landship, desert thunderstorm forming rapidly ahead! They'll navigate for us!
attributes.name: Field Operator

attributes.content: Move move move! We're distancing! Toddifons, Eunectes, find us, stat!
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: Pedal's to the metal already!
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Dammit, you're still not gonna make it! Dump your equipment!
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: There's no time! Dump it!
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: I'll be real here, I've got no faith in prying a second siege ballista out of Closure's pockets.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: We tuned the Raging Ironhide just last week.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Can... *zzzt* respond... *zzzt* ...ditch... landship *zzzt*...
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: Adjusting the guidance system was a pain in the neck.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Engineering's operators put so much blood and sweat into this model revision.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: ...ship...
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: Tch. The line cut out.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: There's a cave in the mountains ahead to the left!
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Want to gamble, Phidia?
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Will it work?
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Gauging how wide the truck is? Should be fine.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: What about everything else?
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: That's what makes it a gamble—
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Hold on tight!
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: So that's what you guys call lucky?
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: We're luckier the storm was small.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: We came back out, we bumped into whoever they were—the Agama Gang. Didn't like the process of beating 'em up, if I'm honest. Might've gone smoother if it was just me, actually.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Hey! It was your fault for shooting your arrows everywhere!
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: I did point out where they were landing. Your fault for dodging too slow.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Why you...
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: We're here.
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: Could've been a moment sooner.
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: Listen up! You're illegally squatting on the property of Resource Reclamation Co., subsidiary of Mama John's. Per Mama John's consumer provisions, we have the right to forcibly evict and counterattack you to a reasonable extent.
attributes.name: Agama Gang Leader

attributes.content: Sir, we've never done a thing to offend anyone! Eaargh!
attributes.name: Wastelander A

attributes.content: M... Mercy! My kids are still here!
attributes.name: Wastelander B

attributes.content: Those bastards...!
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: I see Originium crystals on their skin. All Infected, basically. Careful, enemy's got artillery-type arms too.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: There's fewer wastelanders on the left. I'll penetrate with the Raging Ironhide from that side. That's less accidental casualties.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Alright. Siege ballista erected, preparing to test-fire—
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Round 1 failed. Adjusting position, elevating 3.2 degrees based on point of impact. Using demolishers for Round 2!
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: It's the tough guys HQ told us about! Return fire, return fire, don't let that tractor close in!
attributes.name: Agama Gang Leader

attributes.content: I repeat! She's called the Raging Ironhide—
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Don't be stingy with ammo! Fire every last shell on you!
attributes.name: Agama Gang Leader

attributes.content: Hey, Miss! Careful!
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: Zumama, brake!
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Is that all the firepower you've got? Don't underestimate the Engineering Department Mech Group! This is the fruits of our—
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Uh.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Why did she stop?
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Zumama, back up! I'll cover fire!
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: I'm restarting the engine!
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Miss, your engine's third intake burned out! I've got spare parts! Cover me!
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: Final warning! You are impeding execution of a Mama John's contract!
attributes.name: Agama Gang Leader

attributes.content: Shit. Boss, our cannons are out! That redhead girl shoots like every shot's a miracle!
attributes.name: Agama Gang Member

attributes.content: Zip it, I'll mess that cannoneer up myself. You go take down the snakelet.
attributes.name: Agama Gang Leader

attributes.content: Ready to fire demolisher #4!
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Not on my watch!
attributes.name: Agama Gang Leader

attributes.content: Hah! I'm taking over here, redhead, your supersize bow's a risk to us all! Stand right there and don't move a muscle!
attributes.name: Agama Gang Leader

attributes.content: Well... this gets on my bloody nerves...
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Listen, you hear me? I don't care who you are, or how those wasteland sons of bitches got in contact with you. We're cleaning out the trash here as is lawful and mandated!
attributes.name: Agama Gang Leader

attributes.content: Can you show me your contract a tic?
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Hey, look, we ain't no wild brutes, we're resource reclamation practitioners. Resources mean value, means they deserve to be made use of, e.g. the parts and scrap metal here.
attributes.name: Agama Gang Leader

attributes.content: As for those resources that cannot be reclaimed, we're very sorry, but we will carry out appropriate procedure. I have no personal standing on these wasteland sons of bitches, but the rules are the rules.
attributes.name: Agama Gang Leader

attributes.content: 'Reclaim and exploit: it's the nature of civilization.' That's our company motto, plastered on the wall back at the office.
attributes.name: Agama Gang Leader

attributes.content: If you'd just been honest and told me you're about survival of the fittest, I could've—maybe—given you some respect.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Nobody asked you! Time I taught you a lesson!
attributes.name: Agama Gang Leader

attributes.content: Gah!
attributes.name: Agama Gang Leader

attributes.content: Now you listen to me. You go massacring and call that 'civilization?' You go slitting throats and call that 'reclamation?'
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: You little bitch! I thought you were artillery, what the hell—gaaah!
attributes.name: Agama Gang Leader

attributes.content: That man runs for his life with his bindle and you hound him for fun. That woman tries to save her child and you drag her off by the hair.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: You're just a bunch of gutless nobodies who happened to find yourself some weapons, looking for anyone who's old or weak or ill or bloody impaired enough to have your fun with.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Don't you look down on me—
attributes.name: Agama Gang Leader

attributes.content: Alright, there's a little spine in you. Survival of the fittest then, fist-to-fist, let's go?
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Telling you now, the winner here ain't you.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: You okay, Toddifons?! I'm coming to help!
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Watch how you ride! I got your hunk of junk moving again, that's it! It's not gonna last!
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: That's your lot? Just small-fry? Tch. I was narked, but I think I've shaken it off now!
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Shit, we're in too deep! Pull out, pull out!
attributes.name: Agama Gang Leader

attributes.content: Wow, I bust my ass getting here and it's just over? C'mon, play with me a little.
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: Eek—get outta here, run!
attributes.name: Agama Gang Leader

attributes.content: Is that a wrap?
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: Yeah, they partly scrammed. But they mentioned an agreement between Mama John's and the pasha...?
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: Mama John's won't acknowledge it. Still, we've gotta move these wastelanders ASAP. A couple of Infected are in pretty bad condition.
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: That was pretty risky just now, Toddifons. It's lucky you...
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: What are you doing?!
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Oh, this ballista got its string tension stabilizer sliced off. My guess is it happened when the tractor came in.
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: ...Huh?
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Alright, I'm going to hit you this once and you're going to take it!
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: You busted my hydraulic system earlier!
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Eye for an eye!
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Aren't you gonna do something?
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: ...*sigh*.
attributes.name: Blaze

attributes.content: Er... that's the most repair work I can do you with what I've got, Miss Toddifons. You're probably gonna want to calibrate yourself.
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: This works.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Miss Eunectes, is your engine good?
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: Thanks for your spares. I think repairs are just about done.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Miss Blaze still has some tail-end work to finish. She says she'll meet up with you aboard the landship.
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: Fair.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Understood.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Atmosphere's got me, uh, feeling real awkward right now.
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: Seriously, why won't your barrener lot head to the Rhodes medical post nearby? They've got people sick to death.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: That's the way we live. Ashes to ashes, dust to dust. We came to the wild, so we're bound to return to the wild.
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: Dying to Oripathy's isn't any different from dying to bandits.
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: So you've never longed after... the civilization up on nomadic cities?
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Hah... civilization.
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: We wastelanders are the ones it rejected. We can't go back.
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: But your mechanical handiwork. How did you...?
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Don't ask. Never pry into a wastelander's past life.
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: This settlement did me a favor once, and I returned it as I should. Simple as that.
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: We cross two more dunes ahead and we'll reach the landship.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: About time I parted ways. Thanks for giving me a ride.
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: Hey, redhead.
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: You've got talent.
attributes.name: Rickety Joe

attributes.content: We're back.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Yep... we're back.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: You don't sense it when you're aboard, but seeing it from this angle...
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: ...It really is such a wonder.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: I grew up in the rainforests of Sargon, never coming into contact with any sort of machinery. Everyone lives perfectly fine on their fists alone. One day, I happened to see a nomadic city pass by.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: I'll never forget the hazy, dusky shadow, the faraway rumble that morning. That was the sound of civilization and progress.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: And we're living aboard one of those right now!
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Rhodes Island isn't a nomadic city.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: There's no talking machines in nomadic cities either!
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Hey, Zumama.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Huh?
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: What do you reckon? If I fired off from this distance, would a heavy-duty fortcracker shot make it through Rhodes Island's outer armor?
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Toddifons, if you ever want funds from my master again, I suggest you don't try.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Someone's no fun.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: I was born in Victoria. Family of Vouivre, all immigrated from Sargon. Suppose we're from the same place, come to think. Sometimes my mam would even make Sargon stuff for dinner—supposedly, anyway.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Roast finmeat with plantains?
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Barely as authentic. Just some red pepper tea and what have you...
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: They don't have it easy, Vouivre, finding footing in Victoria. They join the army, or they try blending in with the locals however. My family started running a factory, making... pulleys and stuff.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Not much amazing goes into that. Tear up some scrap, melt down to recast, keep the temperature steady, then pour it into circle molds. Anyone could do that.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: It was like that until my granddad bought this lathe. Naff old second-hand model he got from who knows where, massive, heavy as all, used it for how many years.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: Can you imagine, the first time it started up? It was horrible, obviously, but that massive din and the shaking, all those old parts coming to life... Couldn't even hear my own heartbeat.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: More comforting than fighting ever was, right?
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Bloody right.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: You said civilization and progress... We've never pointed to a lathe and said 'civilization.'
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: It just makes our lives that titchy bit better to live, that's all.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: So, that was your field mission, huh?
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Yes.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: That's not bad! Sounded pretty exciting to me! That red-haired Vouivre, what was she, Toddifons? She sounds like a real rock-hard fist kinda girl!
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: I think you made a new friend!
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Gah, who the hell?!
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Zumama, I got the MK30 of my siege ballista all hammered out! Come to the training ground!
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: You must be Toddifons!
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: Oh, Gavial. I'm here for a go with Eunectes.
attributes.name: Toddifons

attributes.content: She was just telling me she upgraded the Raging Ironhide into the Manic Ironhide! C'mon c'mon c'mon, I'm on break today! You guys fight your hearts out, I'll be there on call, so beat the hell out of each other!
attributes.name: Gavial

attributes.content: ...*sigh*.
attributes.name: Eunectes
